{"tid":400451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6成港人網購　年均花15000港元","createTime":"2017-09-14T20:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T03:49:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c171f540efd4d8f3148b59eb3e97d11be29a246c","tid":400451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170914/photo/bkn-20170914045859810-0914_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170914050424\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170914%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170914045859810-0914_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170914050424&h=17e3ade9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消委會調查發現，現時約有6成港人網購，每年平均花費15000港元。網購令人足不出戶便能搜購服飾、廚具、首飾甚至玩具等，但有不少人表示，曾在網上購物時中伏，被騙而蒙受金錢損失。消委會提醒市民在進行網購時，最好選擇該品牌其下的網站，及其指定的代理網購店，或選擇商譽良好，設有退款及保障機制的大型網購平台。<br />\n<br />\n網店創辦人Trever亦承認，部分網上購物平台令人難辨真偽，買家應該事前做足資料搜集，了解網購平台的背景及信譽。他指，要了解一間網店的信譽，可以從幾方面着手，「例如買家可以睇吓網站嘅聯絡方法多唔多，可靠嘅網店一般會提供多種聯絡方法。」Trever續指，買家應留意網站內貨品的價錢、餘貨數量及買家評語，即使下單後，亦要跟進貨品的送貨進度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170914/bkn-20170914045859810-0914_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170914%2Fbkn-20170914045859810-0914_00822_001.html&d=qsZXs5TePvQudtD6%2FK2izv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=827fd253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170914/bkn-20170914045859810-0914_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dcc2d1455a2780806664dc410b245c336ac89af3","tid":400451,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:57:03.000Z","msg":"7,000,000x0.6x15000=63,000,000,000<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b668634e13c992710cc02f081e8dcbd3ed9e6dc","tid":400451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T01:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6d8a2c0d9967